{"article_id":"oZWUvzUl9iLpGiNb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republicans are eager to exploit the issue .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"House Speaker John A. Boehner has issued a stream of news releases on the emails and the questions","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"he thinks","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"they raise ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"while the House committee","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"investigating the 2012 attacks on the United States mission in Benghazi , Libya ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"has expanded its inquiry","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to include the emails .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"There are still unanswered questions :","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"Who at the State Department advised Mrs. Clinton","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that she could send all her email communications from a private account ?","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"What specific criteria did her lawyers use","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to decide","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"which emails would be deleted on the grounds","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that they were personal ?","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"And what exactly was the classified information","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"government inspectors say","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"was improperly included in her emails ?","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Outside the political maelstrom , some security experts believe","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"the ultimate judgment of her conduct will come not in a court or from Congress but at the ballot box .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"the whole set of circumstances has been scrambled by political considerations","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"surrounding the presidential campaign , \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"said Steven Aftergood , director of the Project on Government Secrecy at the Federation of American Scientists .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"the inadvertent \" spillage \" of classified information into an unclassified system is quite common .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"\" If there ' s a penalty , \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"\" it may cost her some votes . \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Others say","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"more than politics is at stake .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"\" I was stunned to see","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that she didn ' t use the State Department system for State Department business ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"as we were always told","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"we had to do , \"","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"said William Johnson , a former Air Force officer","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"who served at the department from 1999 to 2011 .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Mr. Johnson said","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"his concerns were only compounded by the discovery of classified information in the emails .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" If I ' d done that ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"I ' d be out on bond right now , \"","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"he believed","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that someone should be punished","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"if not Mrs. Clinton ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"then career employees","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"whose job was to safeguard secrets and preserve public records .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"\" It ' s not the end of the world ;","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"she didn ' t give away the crown jewels , \"","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Mr. Johnson said .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"\" But this is not how things are supposed to be done . \"","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"The email controversy breaks into three clear phases :","depth":2},{"id":55,"text":"Mrs. Clinton ' s initial choices","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"about how to set up her email ;","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"her decision","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"to destroy messages","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"she judged to be personal ;","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"and the discovery of classified information in an account","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"where it is not allowed by law .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":123,"left":115,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":80,"right":114,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":69,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":0,"right":68,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":64,"right":67,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":67,"left":65,"right":66,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":65,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":8,"right":78,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":70,"right":77,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":70,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":73,"right":76,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":11,"right":72,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":12,"right":71,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":71,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":15,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":18,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":81,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":113,"left":89,"right":112,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"